---
metadata: {
    partial_name: 'Ecommerce | Banners | Promo Banner Strip'
}
---
{% comment %}
    Sitewide promotional banner strip (website storefront) — rendered above the
    main header. Shows every eligible Promo Banner record: enabled, and (in Liquid)
    within its scheduled window (null start/end = open-ended), in promo_weight ASC
    order. A single eligible banner is static; multiple banners rotate (each shown
    for its own promo_interval_ms) — the rotation, the per-session dismiss cookie
    and the anti-flash hide live in promo-banner.js.

    Include from the website layout, ABOVE the header, gated by the ecommerce_addon
    flag. Kept outside the header fragment cache so the dismiss cookie behaves
    per-request.
{% endcomment %}

{%- graphql banners_res = 'modules/ecommerce/banners/get_eligible_banners' | dig: 'items', 'results' -%}

{%- comment -%} Pass 1: count eligible + build a stable signature of their ids (for the dismiss cookie). {%- endcomment -%}
{%- liquid
    assign now_ts = 'now' | date: '%s' | plus: 0
    assign eligible_count = 0
    assign sig = ''
    for b in banners_res
        assign ok = true
        if b.promo_start_at and b.promo_start_at != blank
            assign start_ts = b.promo_start_at | date: '%s' | plus: 0
            if now_ts < start_ts
                assign ok = false
            endif
        endif
        if b.promo_end_at and b.promo_end_at != blank
            assign end_ts = b.promo_end_at | date: '%s' | plus: 0
            if now_ts > end_ts
                assign ok = false
            endif
        endif
        if ok
            assign eligible_count = eligible_count | plus: 1
            assign sig = sig | append: b.id | append: '-'
        endif
    endfor
-%}

{%- if eligible_count > 0 -%}
{%- comment -%}
    The strip's critical CSS is inlined in the layout <head>
    (modules/website/layout/project_assets, gated by ecommerce_addon) so it paints
    correctly on first paint while the async-loaded ecommerce.css catches up — no
    flash, no layout shift, no JS needed. It lives in <head> (not inline here)
    because <style> is invalid in <body> (W3C). promo-banner.js is deferred.
{%- endcomment -%}
<div class="promo-banner" id="promo-banner" role="region" aria-label="Promotional banner" data-banner-key="{{ sig | escape }}">
    <div class="promo-banner__viewport">
        {%- comment -%} Pass 2: render each eligible banner; first one is active, rest hidden for JS rotation. {%- endcomment -%}
        {%- assign rendered = 0 -%}
        {%- for b in banners_res -%}
            {%- assign ok = true -%}
            {%- if b.promo_start_at and b.promo_start_at != blank -%}
                {%- assign start_ts = b.promo_start_at | date: '%s' | plus: 0 -%}
                {%- if now_ts < start_ts -%}{%- assign ok = false -%}{%- endif -%}
            {%- endif -%}
            {%- if b.promo_end_at and b.promo_end_at != blank -%}
                {%- assign end_ts = b.promo_end_at | date: '%s' | plus: 0 -%}
                {%- if now_ts > end_ts -%}{%- assign ok = false -%}{%- endif -%}
            {%- endif -%}
            {%- if ok -%}
                <div class="promo-banner__slide{% if rendered == 0 %} is-active{% endif %}" data-interval="{{ b.promo_interval_ms | default: 5000 }}" {% if rendered != 0 %}aria-hidden="true"{% endif %}>
                    <span class="promo-banner__message">{{ b.promo_message }}</span>
                    {%- if b.promo_link != blank and b.promo_link_label != blank -%}
                        <a class="promo-banner__link" href="{{ b.promo_link | escape }}">{{ b.promo_link_label }}</a>
                    {%- endif -%}
                </div>
                {%- assign rendered = rendered | plus: 1 -%}
            {%- endif -%}
        {%- endfor -%}
    </div>
    <button type="button" class="promo-banner__close" aria-label="Dismiss banner">
        <span class="icon-close-1" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    </button>
</div>

<script>
    // Anti-flash: hide synchronously (before paint) if already dismissed this session.
    (function () {
        var el = document.getElementById('promo-banner');
        if (!el) return;
        var m = document.cookie.match('(?:^|; )ecom_promo_banner=([^;]*)');
        if (m && decodeURIComponent(m[1]) === el.getAttribute('data-banner-key')) {
            el.style.display = 'none';
        }
    })();
</script>
{%- comment -%} Deferred: rotation/dismiss only — must not block rendering of the page below. {%- endcomment -%}
{%- if context.environment == "staging" -%}
    <script src="{{ 'modules/ecommerce/scripts/promo-banner.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>
{%- else -%}
    <script src="{{ 'modules/ecommerce/scripts/promo-banner.min.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>
{%- endif -%}
{%- endif -%}
